text: Ada County is a county in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 Census, 494,967 people lived in the county. That was more than any other county in Idaho. The county seat and largest city is Boise. Boise is also the state capital. ==Communities== ===Cities=== *Boise *Eagle *Garden City *Kuna *Meridian *Star ===Census-designated places=== *Avimor *Hidden Spring ==References== Category:1864 establishments in Idaho Territory
